    <item>
      <title>除了塑料奶瓶，还有那些对致癌物</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/1120.html</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jun 2011 09:31:54 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/1120.html</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;1、&lt;span style=&#34;WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: medium Simsun; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BORDER-COLLAPSE: separate; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&#34; class=&#34;Apple-style-span&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;FONT-SIZE: 14px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px&#34; class=&#34;Apple-style-span&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;装修少用人造板&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&#34;BORDER-TOP-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; BORDER-LEFT-WIDTH: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14px; BORDER-BOTTOM-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 15px 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT-WIDTH: 0px&#34;&gt;
  室内环境污染主要包括甲醛、苯、甲苯、二 甲苯、苯乙烯及一些放射性氡等物质。它们来自复合板材、油漆、涂料、黏合剂以及地砖等。
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&#34;BORDER-TOP-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; BORDER-LEFT-WIDTH: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14px; BORDER-BOTTOM-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 15px 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT-WIDTH: 0px&#34;&gt;
  　　因此，家庭装修首先要选购合格的装修材料，少用人造板材，别过多使用单一材料；儿童房的家具应以实木为主。装修后，通风一个月再入住。入住前，最好找有资质的权威机构进行检测。住进后，可养铁树、吊兰等植物，以吸收有毒气体。
&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>1、<span style="WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: medium Simsun; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BORDER-COLLAPSE: separate; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" class="Apple-style-span"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px" class="Apple-style-span"><strong>装修少用人造板</strong></span></span></p>
<p style="BORDER-TOP-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; BORDER-LEFT-WIDTH: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14px; BORDER-BOTTOM-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 15px 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT-WIDTH: 0px">
  室内环境污染主要包括甲醛、苯、甲苯、二 甲苯、苯乙烯及一些放射性氡等物质。它们来自复合板材、油漆、涂料、黏合剂以及地砖等。
</p>
<p style="BORDER-TOP-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; BORDER-LEFT-WIDTH: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14px; BORDER-BOTTOM-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 15px 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT-WIDTH: 0px">
  　　因此，家庭装修首先要选购合格的装修材料，少用人造板材，别过多使用单一材料；儿童房的家具应以实木为主。装修后，通风一个月再入住。入住前，最好找有资质的权威机构进行检测。住进后，可养铁树、吊兰等植物，以吸收有毒气体。
</p>
<p style="BORDER-TOP-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; BORDER-LEFT-WIDTH: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14px; BORDER-BOTTOM-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 15px 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT-WIDTH: 0px">
  <p style="BORDER-TOP-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; BORDER-LEFT-WIDTH: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14px; BORDER-BOTTOM-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 15px 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT-WIDTH: 0px">
    2、<span style="WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: medium Simsun; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BORDER-COLLAPSE: separate; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" class="Apple-style-span"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px" class="Apple-style-span"><strong>塑料制品远离热食 <br /><span style="WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: medium Simsun; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BORDER-COLLAPSE: separate; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" class="Apple-style-span"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px" class="Apple-style-span">买前应观察塑料制品底部的三角回收标志，看</span></span></strong></span></span>
  </p>
  <p style="BORDER-TOP-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; BORDER-LEFT-WIDTH: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14px; BORDER-BOTTOM-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 15px 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT-WIDTH: 0px">
    三角形里的数字。通常它有1-7之别，分别代表不同类型成分制成的塑料制品，大多数不耐高温，其中代号为5的多用来制作微波炉饭盒，可耐130度高温，但其盖子通常采用质地透明、代号为7的塑料，也就是用来制作奶瓶的&#8221;危险品&#8221;，最怕受热，应尽量避免盛装热水、热食或被加热。
  </p>
  <p style="BORDER-TOP-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; BORDER-LEFT-WIDTH: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14px; BORDER-BOTTOM-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 15px 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT-WIDTH: 0px">
    <span style="WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: medium Simsun; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BORDER-COLLAPSE: separate; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" class="Apple-style-span"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px" class="Apple-style-span"><strong><span style="WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: medium Simsun; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BORDER-COLLAPSE: separate; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" class="Apple-style-span"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px" class="Apple-style-span"><span style="WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: medium Simsun; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BORDER-COLLAPSE: separate; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" class="Apple-style-span"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px" class="Apple-style-span"><strong>3、不用电热毯 手机 电脑 电视</strong></span></span></span></span></strong></span></span>
  </p>
  <p style="BORDER-TOP-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; BORDER-LEFT-WIDTH: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14px; BORDER-BOTTOM-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 15px 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT-WIDTH: 0px">
    <span style="WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: medium Simsun; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BORDER-COLLAPSE: separate; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" class="Apple-style-span"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px" class="Apple-style-span"><strong><span style="WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: medium Simsun; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BORDER-COLLAPSE: separate; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" class="Apple-style-span"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px" class="Apple-style-span"><span style="WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: medium Simsun; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BORDER-COLLAPSE: separate; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" class="Apple-style-span"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px" class="Apple-style-span"><strong><span style="WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: medium Simsun; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BORDER-COLLAPSE: separate; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" class="Apple-style-span"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px" class="Apple-style-span">在儿童房不要摆电视、电脑，不给孩子用电</span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></strong></span></span>
  </p>
  <p style="BORDER-TOP-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; BORDER-LEFT-WIDTH: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14px; BORDER-BOTTOM-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 15px 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT-WIDTH: 0px">
    热毯。冰箱、微波炉离客厅、卧室越远越好，最好能用墙隔开。使用微波炉时，别让孩子呆在附近。电脑屏幕的背面辐射较强，不要让孩子长时间站在屏幕附近。看电视时，应距离电视机3米以上。
  </p>
  <p style="BORDER-TOP-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; BORDER-LEFT-WIDTH: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14px; BORDER-BOTTOM-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 15px 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT-WIDTH: 0px">
    <span style="WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: medium Simsun; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BORDER-COLLAPSE: separate; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" class="Apple-style-span"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px" class="Apple-style-span"><strong><span style="WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: medium Simsun; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BORDER-COLLAPSE: separate; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" class="Apple-style-span"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px" class="Apple-style-span"><span style="WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: medium Simsun; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BORDER-COLLAPSE: separate; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" class="Apple-style-span"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px" class="Apple-style-span"><strong><span style="WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: medium Simsun; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BORDER-COLLAPSE: separate; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" class="Apple-style-span"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px" class="Apple-style-span">4、<span style="WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: medium Simsun; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BORDER-COLLAPSE: separate; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" class="Apple-style-span"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 14px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px" class="Apple-style-span"><strong>玩具颜色别太艳</strong></span></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></strong></span></span>
  </p>
  <p style="BORDER-TOP-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; BORDER-LEFT-WIDTH: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14px; BORDER-BOTTOM-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 15px 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT-WIDTH: 0px">
    <span style="WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: medium Simsun; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BORDER-COLLAPSE: separate; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" class="Apple-style-span"><strong>儿童玩具中含镉、铅的问题一直存在。一方面，有意添加这类物质后，能使塑料物更坚固。另一方面，金属玩具、涂有彩色颜料的积木、带图案的气球、图书画册等，常会用到喷漆，而有些漆中就含铅。颜崇淮指出，铅是目前公认的影响中枢神经系统发育的环境毒素之一，可以造成多器官、多系统的损伤。</strong></span>
  </p>
  <p style="BORDER-TOP-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; BORDER-LEFT-WIDTH: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14px; BORDER-BOTTOM-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 15px 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT-WIDTH: 0px">
    <p style="BORDER-TOP-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; BORDER-LEFT-WIDTH: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14px; BORDER-BOTTOM-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 15px 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT-WIDTH: 0px">
      　　要避免玩具铅超标问题，首先要保证去正规、信誉好的大商场购买玩具，认准3C合格标识，留意警示语，看清玩具上标明的适宜年龄。别买颜色太鲜艳的。
    </p>
<pre><code>&lt;p style=&quot;BORDER-TOP-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; BORDER-LEFT-WIDTH: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14px; BORDER-BOTTOM-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 15px 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT-WIDTH: 0px&quot;&gt;
  5、&lt;span style=&quot;WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: medium Simsun; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BORDER-COLLAPSE: separate; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot; class=&quot;Apple-style-span&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;FONT-SIZE: 14px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px&quot; class=&quot;Apple-style-span&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;少去地下车库&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;BORDER-TOP-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; BORDER-LEFT-WIDTH: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14px; BORDER-BOTTOM-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 15px 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT-WIDTH: 0px&quot;&gt;
  &lt;span style=&quot;WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: medium Simsun; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BORDER-COLLAPSE: separate; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot; class=&quot;Apple-style-span&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;FONT-SIZE: 14px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px&quot; class=&quot;Apple-style-span&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;WORD-SPACING: 0px; FONT: medium Simsun; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; WHITE-SPACE: normal; LETTER-SPACING: normal; BORDER-COLLAPSE: separate; orphans: 2; widows: 2; webkit-border-horizontal-spacing: 0px; webkit-border-vertical-spacing: 0px; webkit-text-decorations-in-effect: none; webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px&quot; class=&quot;Apple-style-span&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;FONT-SIZE: 14px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px&quot; class=&quot;Apple-style-span&quot;&gt;工业废气、汽车尾气、烟草烟雾、柏油路面受热后&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;BORDER-TOP-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; BORDER-LEFT-WIDTH: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14px; BORDER-BOTTOM-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 15px 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT-WIDTH: 0px&quot;&gt;
  挥发出的气体，以及一些化学清洁剂等中都有毒性，有的甚至致癌。因此，父母首先要避免让孩子吸&amp;#8221;二手烟&amp;#8221;；其次要尽量避开汽车尾气浓度高的地方，比如别在地下车库长时间停留。
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;BORDER-TOP-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; BORDER-LEFT-WIDTH: 0px; FONT-SIZE: 14px; BORDER-BOTTOM-WIDTH: 0px; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; MARGIN: 15px 0px; LINE-HEIGHT: 23px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; BORDER-RIGHT-WIDTH: 0px&quot;&gt;
